an Interesting flavour.

39:47.050 --> 39:48.779
It's brazing.

39:50.780 --> 39:52.145
Notes of citrus.

39:52.190 --> 39:54.818
- My palate isn't
as refined as yours.

40:01.500 --> 40:04.151
itâ€˜s more flavourful
