40:15.880 --> 40:18.576
- What does "frightened"
taste like?

40:20.580 --> 40:23.549
- It's acidic.

40:25.190 --> 40:27.146
- The meat is bitter

40:27.190 --> 40:30.819
about being dead.

40:38.600 --> 40:41.569
- This meat is not pork.

40:48.610 --> 40:50.601
- It's long pig.

41:09.630 --> 41:12.963
You can't reduce me to...

41:13.000 --> 41:15.889
a set of influences.

41:15.940 --> 41:18.602
I'm not the product
of anything.

41:18.640 --> 41:22.076
I've given up
good and evil

41:22.110 --> 41:24.101
for behaviourism.

41:30.550 --> 41:32.814
- Then you can't say
that I'm evil.

41:34.820 --> 41:36.811
- You're destructive.

41:38.830 --> 41:40.718
Same thing.

41:40.760 --> 41:44.594
- Evil is
just destructive?

41:44.630 --> 41:47.861
Storms are evil,
if it's that simple.

41:47.900 --> 41:52.030
And we have fire,
and then there's hail.

41:52.070 --> 41:55.574
Underwriters lump it all
under "Acts of God".

41:59.650 --> 42:02.539
Is this meat
an act of God, Will?

